AUDIO: 'here and I\'m going to clone the Dol Hub getting started from GitHub. I\'ll cd into the folder. Now, first clone a public dot database and I\'m going to run daltsql. Now, we are inside SQL. So, I can run'

[02:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'SQL commands right here in the terminal. Okay, cool. I\'m going to make a small change. And we\'re going to run diff. And this is the first wait, what just happened here'

[02:31] [scene:talk]
